cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper deals with accelerating semantic segmentation on video, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a new feature estimation scheme, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.RO (Robotics). Finally, the paper deals with video compression techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
